name: Outside Inside Backpack Harmonica
description: A harmonica for the aspiring backcountry Alan Wilson. The tough design goes with you to the campsite or cabin, and it includes a mini manual to help you jump start your music career.10-hole octave harmonica.C-key.Brass reeds and ABS comb.Stainless steel covers with a matte finish give a sleek look.Includes cleaning cloth and a protective carrying pouch.Comes with a booklet of tips to help you master the harmonica.
